# Stage 1 mandatory workflow

Before making any code changes, you must first read these files:

- docs/ai/IMPLEMENTATION_GUIDE_FOR_STAGE1.md
- docs/ai/CLAUDE_CURSOR_RULES.md
- docs/ai/STAGE1_MASTER_PLAN_SYNTHESIS.md

Then inspect the relevant code before proposing edits.

Follow these project priorities strictly:
1. reliability
2. grounded answers
3. simplicity for business analysts
4. low CPU/RAM load on the current laptop
5. future extensibility only if it adds near-zero current complexity

Default policy:
- prefer deterministic logic over LLM logic
- prefer disabling heavy features over tuning around them
- keep one main user flow in public UI
- keep changes small and commit-friendly
- explain touched files before editing
- provide verification steps after editing